data.description: The home exudes Old Florida Charm. Enjoy ocean access boating in this This beautiful 3/2 w/ office/den CBS home & 2020 metal roof is situated on a very private 1/2+ acre lot surrounded located in Mariner's Landing. Mariners Landing offers ocean access from the community boat ramp and day dock. The home is nestled into the lush tropical landscaping and preserve. The vaulted ceilings give this home an open airy feeling. Kitchen features a cozy breakfast nook. The split plan provides privacy for the primary suite.  The home features beautiful cypress paneling, a very large covered porch with vaulted ceilings, hot tub, fire pit and tranquil fountains.  The back yard is like a nature preserve featuring a gazebo, Florida natural sculpture garden, and fruit trees (mango, carambola, banana, avocado, guava & orange). The detached building is perfect for a man cave, she-shed, studio or office.  There is boat or RV parking on the side of the house.  So private and secluded yet close to everything! Come take a look!  The low yearly HOA fee (only $300.00) includes use of community boat ramp and dock. This is a unique boating community sits on the South Fork of the St Lucie River and has easy access to I95 & downtown Stuart.  Available furnished or unfurnished.
